---
title: The Lucky Duck Pulled Hoisin Duck Burger, Spicy Smacked Cucumber, Chips and Garlic Mayo
description: Nothing says ‘taste adventure’ like The Lucky Duck – Pulled Hoisin Duck Burger, Spicy Smacked Cucumber, Chips and Garlic Mayo. This one brings spicy and sticky-sweet flavours together.
